# Both Dockerfiles `COPY . .` into their build stage; without this the build
# context ships the host's `target/` (gigabytes, invalidating the layer cache
# on every local build) and `.git/` — neither belongs in an image build, and a
# hermetic build should see only the sources `cargo build --locked` needs.
target/
.git/
.github/
docs/
deployment/
infra/
*.md
